{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act22side", "eventName": "照我以火", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "FC-ST-3", "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "一聲嗚咽", "storyInfo": "在即將到來的戰爭面前，每個人的生活都易碎無比。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g11_hispdwarshipdeck", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$mist_loop", "key": "$mist_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "前方小雨天氣，航道已確認，沿途偵測站將默認放行。", "name": "電台通訊聲"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "收到道森子爵的電報，對方希望借此次放行的契機，與深池代表會面。", "name": "電台通訊聲"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$transmission", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1", "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_723_1#7$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "又是一些倒向我們的貴族。", "name": "“校官”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#7$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_723_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放心吧，領袖不打算對他們有什麼表示。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#7", "name2": "avg_npc_723_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是簡單示好就想獲得深池的和平保證，控制住領地內塔拉人的激昂情緒，是不是有點太吝嗇了？", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#7"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們遲早要學會，怎麼付出代價才算誠意十足。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#7"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#7", "name2": "avg_npc_723_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "領袖依然派你去交涉？", "name": "“校官”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#8$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_723_1#8$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許我更需要花一段時間，讓大家先忘記我。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是個好消息。以我的標準，你失誤的行動不少。", "name": "“校官”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵呵......既然你獨自登艦彙報，看來，你還是沒抓到拉芙希妮。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不必明知故問。", "name": "“校官”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你阻攔了我的隊伍繼續搜捕，事後又把她去過的地點暗示給我的士兵，這種搭救方式於你而言，算不上高明。", "name": "“校官”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你又怎麼知道，我搭救的不是你呢？", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我記得，領袖從來沒有說過自己想處死她吧？", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "領袖允許她肆意逃竄，也同樣允許我自行判斷，要如何對待她。", "name": "“校官”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不要怪我對你的熟人太過苛刻，阿赫茉妮。沒人能放任一條德拉克在眼下的維多利亞隨意行動。", "name": "“校官”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別在意，我想我和她的關係也沒有那麼好。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你瞧，我正打算去她此前藏身的那家醫療公司看看。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵呵，也說不定，先抓到她的人是我呢。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_241"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......喂，等等，航道上有建築物？能見度太低，發現得太晚了！", "name": "維多利亞軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這一帶的航道規劃是誰完成的？前天的勘測組是哪一組？", "name": "維多利亞軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在全艦隊偏轉方向已經來不及了，優先確認建築內有無人員。", "name": "維多利亞軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......好。磚木結構房屋，體積很小，不會對戰艦履帶造成任何威脅。按照原定航道繼續行駛。", "name": "維多利亞軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#7", "name2": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......啊，又是一個小小的失誤。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#7"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#7", "name2": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戰爭總要忍受一些犧牲。", "name": "“校官”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#7", "name2": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我明白你的意思。但是，我也有我的“自行判斷”。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#7"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓拉芙希妮犧牲？代價恐怕太大了。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#7"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "畢竟，那可是流著德拉克之血的戰士，就算感染了礦石病，也還是很有用呢。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g6_noblelivingroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，我沒有將她帶回來。", "name": "“校官”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她沒有戰鬥的決心，反而很擅長逃亡。", "name": "“校官”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_723_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "另外......我們追蹤到了她進入塔拉王城舊址的痕跡。遺跡內的火熄滅了。", "name": "“校官”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#6$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "成為感染者，或許讓她的源石技藝發生了變化。", "name": "“校官”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#6$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_722_1#1$1", "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你似乎認為，是礦石病增強了她的力量？", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_722_1#1$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵呵......當然不。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_722_1#1$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她是我的妹妹，要是連與我稍微抗衡的力量都沒有，那才實在是令人失望。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_722_1#1$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "告訴我，她身邊有誰？", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_722_1#1$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有幾個流民跟在她身邊，她在那些人面前堅持自稱領袖。", "name": "“校官”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_722_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，你就不用跟著她了。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_722_1#1$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然她終於醒來，意識到自己作為德拉克的權能......", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_722_1#1$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那她很快就會回到我身邊。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_722_1#1$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "21_G7_decisivebattlealley_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_dia_street_intro", "key": "$m_dia_street_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_662_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1", "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_662_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你確定能從這裡搭長途貨車？", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_662_1#6$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_662_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是呀，我以前逃出維多利亞的時候就坐過。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_662_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......風笛。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你記不記得，我之前就問過你，你想要的真相是什麼，以及，知道之後你又想做什麼。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其實這個結果，你早該知道。維多利亞的許多事情，最終大抵是這樣的權力鬥爭。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，話是這樣說......可是每一件事裡，被捲進去的還是不一樣的人。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的想法還是沒有變，我必須把自己的報告書遞出去。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只不過，我在想，什麼時候維多利亞才會有一個地方能真正收下這份報告書？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我到底能用自己的雙手做些什麼，來讓維多利亞快些變成這樣的地方？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_662_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "經歷了這麼多事，你還是想要改變維多利亞？你還真是......", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_662_1#8$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_662_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真什麼？真傻，還是真倔？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_662_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......真頑強。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_662_1#8$1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_662_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#9", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這也是為什麼我們一直都是好朋友吧？認定的目標輕易不會改變，陳陳，我跟你，跟隊長，都是一樣的欸！", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#9"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_662_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#9", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈。從你嘴裡說出來，就不像誇我。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_662_1#8$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_662_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有，這些天其實我也一直在想......誰也不能說別人的夢想，是一定不能實現的吧？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_662_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$transmission", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（無信號的嗞嗞聲）", "name": "收音機"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_662_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你還留著維恩塞給你的這東西。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_662_1#6$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_662_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，不奇怪吧？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_662_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我來吧，這收音機已經夠舊了，我真怕在你手裡變成一堆廢鐵。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_662_1#8$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_doorknob", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_devicebeep", "volume": 1.0, "delay": 0.4}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_662_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好了。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_662_1#8$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$transmission", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......全體領民注意，維多利亞與卡茲戴爾在倫蒂尼姆周邊衝突不斷升級......", "name": "收音機"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戰爭......嗞嗞......爆發......", "name": "收音機"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "威靈頓公爵......嗞嗞......", "name": "收音機"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請做好戰爭準備......", "name": "收音機"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g1_victoriavillage", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$ponder_intro", "key": "$ponder_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1", "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是，我正在駕車返回，偵察任務已經完成，沒有發現異常動向。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "之前那個身份所用的辦公室？返程後我會第一時間銷毀所有痕跡，請放心。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#10$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果沒有意外，我當然會接受公爵授予我的提拔。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這種事我並不打算隱瞞。到了那時，我個人的身份與面貌都會被拋棄掉，以現在的身份對你講什麼，都不重要吧？", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$transmission", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#6$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "下車走走吧。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_725_1#8$1", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎，先生，要木人嗎？我從河那邊的聚落帶來的，奶奶的手藝可精湛了。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#8$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好......請問，你是這附近的人嗎？", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......什麼事？", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#10$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_725_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，感覺你看起來有點眼熟？真不好意思，我剛到這裡落腳，還沒認清這一帶的人呢。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#8$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我叫維恩，賣東西的。要是你有想買想賣的，都可以跟我說一聲，我順路給你帶上。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#8$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我住在那邊，你看，昨天剛建好的屋子。離聚落是遠了一點，但在大路旁邊，我覺得不壞。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#8$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸，這是你的車啊......我認錯人了？", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真不好意思，打擾您散心了，那您繼續——", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$smallearthquake", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_autocannon", "volume": 0.8, "delay": 0.2}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 2.5, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "巨大的轟鳴聲讓兩個人同時轉過頭。"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "龐大的影子浮現在地平線，他們腳下的地面不住顫抖。"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#5$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_725_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......那個聲音是，什麼東西？", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#4$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不不不，那是什麼？", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#4$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_725_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......軍隊？", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#5$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......昨天，我在四百公里外完成了對這支部隊的偵察任務。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#5$1"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_725_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你這是在說什麼？", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#5$1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我始終相信，以強硬軍事手段著稱的鐵公爵，是我們最大的敵人。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#5$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在他的支持下，深池煽動民眾的仇恨，將無辜的普通人拖入暴亂甚至全面戰爭之中。我們必須找到與他制衡的方法。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#5$1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的每一次行動，都牽扯著成百上千的普通人的性命。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是現在......", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他發現自己無法再發出聲音。"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "轟隆。轟隆。"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "高速戰艦率領的戰鬥集群行駛在它既定的航道上。"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡是開斯特公爵的領地。她默許了這一切發生，默許了戰爭借她的道路進發，碾過維多利亞的土地。"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......逃吧，塔拉人。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的房子建錯了地方。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_725_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為、為什麼？", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#5$1"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這一帶仍然是開斯特公爵的領地，你們還沒越過那條模糊的邊界。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "經過這一段時間的周旋後，特倫特侯爵終究沒有倒向威靈頓公爵，並且，對塔拉人的管理會再度加壓。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就在這兩天，或許你就會重新遇見那些粗暴的巡邏隊，或許他們還沒有忘記你這張臉曾經出現在案宗裡。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他是不是猜錯了公爵的意思？他會不會也成為這場戰爭中被犧牲的一枚棋子？", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#6$1"}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們誰都無法回答。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#7$1"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......若是我們能知道答案，那孤獨的小屋就不會建在錯誤的位置了。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#7$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_725_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，您在說什麼呀......", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#5$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_725_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——等等，我想起來了，你、你是那個時候來抓我們的人！", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#4$1"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 12.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你、你要幹什麼......", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#4$1"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cardoorc", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$sportscarstart", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "菲舍爾沒有回答，只是轉身上了車，啟動了引擎。"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在他身後，磚瓦小屋崩塌的聲音和鄉民悲痛的一聲叫喊，都被淹沒在高速戰艦的噪音裡。"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 4.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}